race.description: Sportsbet Set A Deposit Limit Handicap (56)
race.comment: Tricky race to close proceedings. IRONBAR (3) looks to be going the best of a bunch who don't win out of turn. He's been warming into his races late and caught the eye here last start when surging into third. He'll likely drift back again from the draw, but the rise in trip is perfect for him to reel them in. PRODIGAL LAD (7) hasn't threatened this prep but gets a very welcome drop in grade and steps out to a preferred journey. Toeroek's booking is a clear signal of intent. A bold showing is on the cards. IN YOUR WORDS (10) closed strongly to just miss at Naracoorte. If Hutchinson can make better use of the draw, she can go a couple better. HARD LEAF (4) comes through the same race and was solid without threatening first-up. He'll be fitter now and is drawn to get every favour.
